member.summary:
 Compartmentalized message rate throttler class.
 This class should be used when wishing to throttle a message rate, but do other work than sleep when it is not
 presently possible to send.
 
  For example:

  CompartmentalizedMessageRateThrottler compartmentalizedMessageRateThrottler;
  ...
  while (true) 
  {
      if (0 == compartmentalizedMessageRateThrottler.InactivityPeriod) 
      {
          // Send a message.
          MyPostMessage();
          compartmentalizedMessageRateThrottler.Complete();
      }
      else 
      {
          // Do some other work for a while.
          ...
      }
  }

members.member:
Match a string against the pattern.
@param str the string to match.
@param fromPart which part of the pattern to match from.
@return	true if matches.

Get a part of the pattern.
@param index index of the part of the pattern to return.
@return	Pattern section.

member.param:
if true, the SyncRequestId will be disposed automatically in getResponse(s) when
timeout occurs or response is complete and no messages remain.
if false it will be user's responsibility to dispose the object by calling dispose()
